1
00:00:00,506 --> 00:00:02,005
Srila Guru Maharaj

2
00:00:02,005 --> 00:00:04,220
when he was speaking about Giriraj Govardhan

3
00:00:04,220 --> 00:00:07,346
the Govardhan Shila  he said:

4
00:00:08,224 --> 00:00:13,760
“His position is similar to Mahaprabhu”.

5
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,552
Jiva Goswami

6
00:00:15,567 --> 00:00:21,290
in describing Chaitanya Mahaprabhu he says:

7
00:00:28,545 --> 00:00:35,818
“Internally Krishna, externally as Gaura,

8
00:00:35,818 --> 00:00:42,591
internally Krishna, externally in the mood of the servitor”.

9
00:00:42,591 --> 00:00:44,695
Even the person in this world

10
00:00:44,695 --> 00:00:49,819
can simultaneously hold different identities,

11
00:00:49,819 --> 00:00:54,447
like a girl can be a daughter,

12
00:00:54,447 --> 00:01:00,562
a sister, a mother, a wife.

13
00:01:00,562 --> 00:01:05,007
She can hold those positions all simultaneously.

14
00:01:05,007 --> 00:01:07,704
From one group, or one perspective,

15
00:01:07,704 --> 00:01:11,521
the sister, the mother, the wife, the daughter –

16
00:01:11,521 --> 00:01:13,240
it is all possible.

17
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:16,225
So that Krishna

18
00:01:16,225 --> 00:01:18,334
in all of his Divine Manifestations

19
00:01:18,334 --> 00:01:27,881
can hold multiple positions is not intangible?

20
00:01:27,881 --> 00:01:29,365
And following the principle of that –

21
00:01:29,365 --> 00:01:31,971
a part of the infinite is the infinite.

22
00:01:31,971 --> 00:01:37,167
So we take one stone from Govardhan Hill

23
00:01:37,167 --> 00:01:42,883
and it’s the whole Govardhan Hill, it is completely Krishna.

24
00:01:42,883 --> 00:01:49,463
That is Achintya Shakti, His inconceivable potency.

25
00:01:50,217 --> 00:01:54,170
Yet, sometimes Radha Khunda is considered

26
00:01:54,170 --> 00:01:56,173
the representation of Radharani,

27
00:01:56,173 --> 00:01:59,339
Govardhan - the representation of Krishna,

28
00:01:59,339 --> 00:02:02,080
many different things to be considered.

29
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:07,414
So in conclusion we will say, achintya beda bed.

30
00:02:07,414 --> 00:02:10,004
Or as the Thai people say:

31
00:02:10,004 --> 00:02:14,336
“Same same, but different”.

32
00:02:14,353 --> 00:02:18,534
Krishna, and devotee of Krishna.

33
00:02:21,209 --> 00:02:26,033
As Mahaprabhu is Krishna, and devotee of Krishna.

34
00:02:28,846 --> 00:02:32,052
But He descended for Bhakta Bhav

35
00:02:32,052 --> 00:02:34,849
and ultimately Radha Bhav

36
00:02:34,849 --> 00:02:39,444
Bhakta Bhav - devotee of Krishna mentality,

37
00:02:39,444 --> 00:02:42,433
and Radharani - Radha Bhav.

38
00:02:49,116 --> 00:02:55,351
So in this way there is an intimate connection between

39
00:02:55,351 --> 00:02:58,757
Sri Krishna Chaitanya Mahaprabhu and Giriraj Govardhan.

